T1  - Markets for risk and openness to trade: how are they related?
AU  - Svaleryd, Helena
AU  - Vlachos, Jonas
JO  - Journal of International Economics
VL  - 57
IS  - 2
SP  - 369
EP  - 395
PY  - 2002
DA  - 2002/08/01/
